name: Knockout
note:
State #1 will be automatically added when
HP reaches 0.

name: Frozen
note:
<Custom Respond Effect>
var fire = 4;
if (this.isPhysical() && target.result().hpDamage > 0) {
  target.setHp(0);
} else if (this.item().damage.elementId === fire) {
  var stateId = 13;
  target.removeState(stateId);
}
</Custom Respond Effect>

name: Endure
note:
<Custom React Effect>
// Check to see if the party is in battle.
if ($gameParty.inBattle()) {
  // Sets the flag if the target has more than 1 HP at the time of death.
  target._secondChance = target.hp > 1;
}
</Custom React Effect>

<Custom Respond Effect>
// Check to see if the party is in battle, has the Second Chance flag, and if the target is dead with 0 HP.
if ($gameParty.inBattle() && target._secondChance && target.hp <= 0) {
  // Play the revival animation.
  target.startAnimation(49);
  // Set the target's HP to 1.
  target.setHp(1);
}
</Custom Respond Effect>

name: Critical Protect
note:
<Custom Battle Effect>
user._criticalProtect = false;
</Custom Battle Effect>

<Custom Victory Effect>
user._criticalProtect = false;
</Custom Victory Effect>

<Custom Escape Effect>
user._criticalProtect = false;
</Custom Escape Effect>

<Custom Defeat Effect>
user._criticalProtect = false;
</Custom Defeat Effect>

<Custom Respond Effect>
var crisis = 0.25;
if ($gameParty.inBattle() && target.isAlive() && target.hpRate() <= crisis && !target._criticalProtect) {
  target._criticalProtect = true;
  var turns = 5;
  // Adds DEF (ID: 3) buff to target.
  target.addBuff(3, turns);
  target.startAnimation(53);
}
</Custom Respond Effect>
